author: Meg Cunningham
title: Trump's message to 'liberate' states dangerous: Washington Gov. Jay Inslee
description: Washington Gov. Jay Inslee appeared Sunday on ABC’s “This Week.”
content:
President Donald Trump's message to liberate states, as some Americans gather to protest stay-at-home orders, is basically encouraging illegal activity, Washington Gov. Jay Inslee said Sunday on ABCs This Week.
